" School of Webcraft is a free, online community for learning open web development. We think that learning with other people is the best way to help you learn the skills and theory to create web sites and apps using up-to-date open web technologies.

At School of Webcraft you can start learning web development right away. We offer peer-driven study groups and courses driven by learners just like you."
